---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<MainLayout title="Network as a Service (NaaS) | Blue Cap IT" description="Network as a Service from Blue Cap IT — your entire enterprise network delivered as one monthly subscription. Hardware, installation, software, ISP management, and 24/7 operations included. No upfront costs.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <img src="/images/naas-hero.jpg" alt="Fiber optic light radiating outward — symbolizing enterprise network connectivity" style="width:100%;height:auto;max-height:340px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:1rem;margin-bottom:2rem;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);" />
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> Network as a Service</div>
      <div class="section-label">What We Do</div>
      <h1>Network as a <span class="grad">Service.</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Stop buying hardware, hiring network specialists, and juggling ISP contracts. Blue Cap IT delivers your entire enterprise network — design, hardware, installation, software, ISP management, and 24/7 operations — as a single monthly subscription. Zero upfront costs. Zero complexity.</p>
      <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- WHY NAAS -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Why NaaS</div>
          <h2>A Smarter Way<br/><span class="grad">to Run Your Network.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Most businesses piece together networking from multiple vendors — buying switches, hiring engineers, and managing ISP contracts on their own. Network as a Service replaces all of that with one integrated solution: enterprise-grade hardware, intelligent software, professional installation, and ongoing management — delivered as a simple monthly subscription.</p>
          <p class="section-sub" style="margin-top:1rem;">Blue Cap IT designs, deploys, and manages your network so you get enterprise-grade connectivity without enterprise-grade headaches.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:wallet" /></div>
            <div><h4>No Upfront Hardware Costs</h4><p>Pay one predictable monthly subscription based on your space and usage. No capital expense, no depreciation cycles, no surprise hardware refreshes.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:layers" /></div>
            <div><h4>Full-Stack Solution</h4><p>Switches, Wi-Fi access points, firewalls, cellular gateways, software, installation, and ongoing management — all from one provider. No more multi-vendor finger-pointing.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:bot" /></div>
            <div><h4>AI-Powered Management</h4><p>Modern NaaS platforms use generative AI to build dashboards, troubleshoot issues, and answer network questions — all from a natural language interface. No CLI required.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:settings-2" /></div>
            <div><h4>Hands-Free Operations</h4><p>From ISP negotiations to network design to proactive monitoring and patching — your NaaS provider handles the complexity so your team can focus on the business.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IMAGE BAND -->
  <section style="padding:0 4% 4rem;">
    <div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;">
      <img src="/images/naas-network.jpg" alt="Modern data center server rack with neatly organized network cabling" style="width:100%;height:auto;max-height:380px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:1rem;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">How It Works</div>
        <h2>From Design <span class="grad">to Done.</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0.8rem auto 0;text-align:center;">Network as a Service handles every step of your network — from planning to installation to ongoing management. Here's the process from day one through year ten.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));">
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:pencil-ruler" /></div>
          <h3>1. Network Design</h3>
          <p>An expert engineering team designs a network tailored to your space, devices, and performance needs — heat maps, port counts, redundancy plans included.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:plug-zap" /></div>
          <h3>2. Professional Install</h3>
          <p>Hardware, cabling, configuration, and testing — handled end-to-end. Your team stays focused on the business; the install just happens.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:globe" /></div>
          <h3>3. ISP Management</h3>
          <p>Negotiating with internet providers, managing contracts, coordinating installs and renewals — all handled for you. One bill, one point of contact.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:activity" /></div>
          <h3>4. Ongoing Operations</h3>
          <p>Proactive monitoring, automatic firmware updates, expert support, and continuous optimization keep your network running at peak performance — 24/7.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT'S INCLUDED -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">What's Included</div>
        <h2>Everything Your<br/><span class="grad">Network Needs.</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0.8rem auto 0;text-align:center;">Network as a Service includes every layer of modern enterprise networking. No add-ons, no surprises — just one subscription that covers it all.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));">
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:network" /></div>
          <h3>Enterprise Switches</h3>
          <p>PoE++ switches with multi-gigabit ports and high-speed uplinks. Silent, compact, and cloud-managed — built for modern offices, warehouses, and campuses.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:wifi" /></div>
          <h3>Wi-Fi 7 Access Points</h3>
          <p>Tri-band wireless access points engineered for high-density environments. Consistent coverage, fast roaming, and the latest Wi-Fi standards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:shield-check" /></div>
          <h3>Firewalls</h3>
          <p>Enterprise-grade firewalls with automatic failover, deep packet inspection, VPN, and SD-WAN — security and performance without the complexity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:radio-tower" /></div>
          <h3>5G Cellular Gateway</h3>
          <p>High-speed cellular failover and out-of-band management. Keeps your business connected even when wired internet drops.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:layout-dashboard" /></div>
          <h3>AI-Powered Dashboard</h3>
          <p>A single pane of glass for your entire network. Natural language controls, real-time monitoring, custom dashboards, and intelligent troubleshooting.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:wrench" /></div>
          <h3>Install &amp; 24/7 Support</h3>
          <p>Professional installation, proactive monitoring, automatic updates, and expert support — bundled into your monthly subscription. No truck-roll fees.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY BLUE CAP IT -->
  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Why Blue Cap IT</div>
          <h2>Local Partner.<br/><span class="grad">Enterprise Network.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Blue Cap IT delivers Network as a Service backed by best-in-class enterprise networking technology. You get the simplicity of NaaS plus a local partner who knows your business, your systems, and your goals — and answers the phone when you call.</p>
          <p class="section-sub" style="margin-top:1rem;">We handle the design, the install, the day-to-day operations, and the long-term strategy — so your team can focus on the work that actually moves your business forward.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
            <a href="about.html" class="btn-ghost">About Blue Cap IT</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:zap" /></div>
            <div><h4>Fast, Local Support</h4><p>A real person who knows your network — not a ticket queue in another time zone. Call (410) 858-4031 and you'll talk to someone who can actually help.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:cog" /></div>
            <div><h4>End-to-End Delivery</h4><p>We handle the network assessment, design, install, cutover, and ongoing operations — from the first walk-through to year ten of your subscription.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:handshake" /></div>
            <div><h4>One IT Partner</h4><p>Blue Cap IT also delivers managed IT, cybersecurity, and physical security. NaaS plugs into a complete IT stack — no juggling vendors.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:clipboard-list" /></div>
            <div><h4>Existing Hardware Buyback</h4><p>Already invested in network gear? We can help you transition. Buyback programs and migration plans available — talk to us about your existing setup.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA FOOTER -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
      <div class="section-label">Get Started</div>
      <h2>Ready to Switch to <span class="grad">Network as a Service?</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub" style="max-width:640px;margin:0.8rem auto 2rem;text-align:center;">Contact Blue Cap IT for a free network assessment. We'll evaluate your current setup, map out a NaaS plan, and show you what your monthly subscription would look like — with zero pressure and zero upfront cost.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">Call (410) 858-4031</a>
        <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" class="btn-ghost">info@bluecapit.com</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
